{"tid":1912480,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"區議員會唔會設立連儂牆？","createTime":"2020-03-06T06:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T09:14:27.000Z","uid":173326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"29b518615a430dc826af4e78027097cb5262ed30","tid":1912480,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:08:55.000Z","msg":"好似黃店外牆咁，可以安全貼文宣，又唔驚俾食環剷走"},{"pid":"2b2085440ccf0980306ec5332815fa9d2761495b","tid":1912480,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc62925fc622c4cbd87f140f47fb18be8678bf0","tid":1912480,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d704c2c2efa684a7fef51efe2d07658472939bf3","tid":1912480,"uid":247032,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:20:16.000Z","msg":"如果想區議會做 要諗下點玩權力同遊戲規則<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民主派離島區議員王進洋早前問及房屋署及食環署會否遵循《基本法》第27條列明，香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版自由，盡最大努力於區內設連儂牆，房署於今日離島區議會第二次會議提交書面回覆，表明現不考慮設立特定展示地點供公眾張貼一些毋須申請的展示品，<strong>食環署更稱增設「連儂牆」會「影響社會回復和諧及安全的進程」，相關違法個案更會「影響香港的國際形象」</strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食環拒研設連儂牆 反斥損社會回復安全進程 (2020-03-02)<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200302/A4KWBYUMGZ6YTIJKKHOSKOLCOA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200302%2FA4KWBYUMGZ6YTIJKKHOSKOLCOA%2F&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcFcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=424bd0ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200302%2FA4KWBYUMGZ6YTIJKKHOSKOLCOA%2F&h=aae5ef93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">h